Kraft Foods Inc

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

This article is about the original company that became Mondelēz International following the 2012 split. For the post-split company also called Kraft Foods, see Kraft Foods.
Not to be confused with The Kraft Group.

